--- !u!114 &2033000230
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 2033000229}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3e62d9a51c5d07c4d9f7693e72174efd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CutsceneController
  panels:
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2541569950480670820, guid: c3cdb17d47623864b91cb8e1f8956bd2, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "I need to navigate these corridors to the castle\u2019s heart\u2026
      only then can I break this curse. \n\nBut right now i must hide i hear voices
      approaching."
    characterPortrait: {fileID: -6619754007301896981, guid: e15d77dd72b0a4f499b553ec15e516bf, type: 3}
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: -7896857417374089885, guid: 84f3a1fe8b7f9ff4da1da9bed20bf972, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rakel
    bodyText: "I am in possession of this fickle witch\u2019s body\u2026 and the
      minds of all living and not things in this castle. \n\nOr so I thought."
    characterPortrait: {fileID: -7881499446659708881, guid: 23aa52fac008cb847b1410c933ba4703, type: 3}
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 7235246989575666249, guid: 026ddea7c40a138469f56f4b41bfb893, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rakel
    bodyText: "You useless guards cannot even direct your eyes in the right direction.
      \n\nMust I do all the hard work myself?"
    characterPortrait: {fileID: -6619754007301896981, guid: e15d77dd72b0a4f499b553ec15e516bf, type: 3}
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: -3203018267053999313, guid: 1de27a4b4d967bc42a63a72d73817b76, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rakel
    bodyText: "I can hear your pleas for mercy, your apologies echoing in your mind\u2026
      but I care not for your thoughts or words. Prove yourself through action. Catch
      me that imposter, or you will share the fate of the witches imprisoned in the
      dungeon. \n\nThe intruders have made it into my corridors\u2026 you had better
      catch them!"
    characterPortrait: {fileID: -7881499446659708881, guid: 23aa52fac008cb847b1410c933ba4703, type: 3}
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: -1297384860562760380, guid: d42bb011bfbe66a498b018f2c646fbf1, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "Power made her reckless\u2026 and now it binds her to this curse.
      But maybe she can still be freed, her soul, and the souls of all trapped within
      these walls. \n\nIf I break the castle\u2019s hold, none of them need remain
      prisoners."
    characterPortrait: {fileID: -6619754007301896981, guid: e15d77dd72b0a4f499b553ec15e516bf, type: 3}
  nextSceneName: Level3_Corridors
